quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,163,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu, kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé mi."
  26,164,"Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  26,165,"Ṣé àwọn ọkùnrin nínú ẹ̀dá ni ẹ̀yin ọkùnrin yóò lọ máa bá (fún adùn ìbálòpọ̀)?"
  30,55,"Àti pé ní ọjọ́ tí Àkókò náà bá ṣẹlẹ̀ (ìyẹn, ọjọ́ Àjíǹde), àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ yóò máa búra pé àwọn kò gbé (ilé ayé) ju àkókò kan lọ.” Báyẹn ni wọ́n ṣe máa ń ṣẹ́rí wọn kúrò níbi òdodo."
  30,56,"Àwọn tí A fún ní ìmọ̀ àti ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo yóò sọ pé: “Dájúdájú nínú àkọsílẹ̀ ti Allāhu, ẹ ti gbé ilé ayé títí Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde (fi tó). Nítorí náà, èyí ni Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde, ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀yin kò mọ̀.”"
  30,57,"Nítorí náà ní ọjọ́ yẹn, àwọn tó ṣàbòsí, àwáwí wọn kò níí ṣe wọ́n ní àǹfààní. Wọn kò sì níí fún wọn ní àyè láti ṣe ohun tí wọn yóò fi rí ìyọ́nú Allāhu."
  32,25,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Ó máa ṣe ìdájọ́ láààrin wọn ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń yapa-ẹnu lórí rẹ̀."
  32,26,"Ṣé kò fojú hàn sí wọn pé, mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Àwọn náà sì ń rìn kọjá nínú àwọn ibùgbé wọn! Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Nítorí náà, ṣé wọn kò níí tẹ́tí gbọ́rọ̀ (òdodo ni)?"
  32,27,"Tàbí wọn kò rí i pé dájúdájú Àwa l’À ń wa omi òjò lọ sórí ilẹ̀ gbígbẹ, tí A sì ń fi mú irúgbìn jáde? Àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn wọn àti àwọn náà sì ń jẹ nínú rẹ̀. Nítorí náà, ṣé wọn kò ríran ni?"
  33,16,"Sọ pé: “Síságun yín kò lè ṣe yín ní àǹfààní, tí ẹ bá sá fún ikú tàbí pípa (sí ojú ogun ẹ̀sìn. Tí ẹ bá sì ságun) nígbà náà, A kò níí fún yín ní ìgbádùn ayé bí kò ṣe fún ìgbà díẹ̀."
  33,17,"Sọ pé: “Ta ni ẹni tí ó lè dá ààbò bò yín lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu tí Ó bá fẹ́ fi aburú kàn yín tàbí tí Ó bá fẹ́ kẹ yín?” Wọn kò sì lè rí aláàbò tàbí alárànṣe kan lẹ́yìn Allāhu."
  33,18,"Dájúdájú Allāhu ti mọ àwọn tó ń fa ènìyàn sẹ́yìn nínú yín àti àwọn tó ń wí fún àwọn arakùnrin wọn pé: “Ẹ máa bọ̀ wá sí ọ̀dọ̀ wa.” Wọn kò sì níí lọ sí ojú ogun ẹ̀sìn àfi (ogun) díẹ̀."